  "detailed_description": "Mining Odyssey is a dynamic platformer game in first person view.<br><br>Take your pickaxe and grappling gun and challenge 15 successive timed trials, in which you will have to gather a set list of ores in a hostile environment.<br><br>Explore, discover, memorize, die and retry. With each try, get closer to your goal and dive deeper in harder trials.<br><br>Triumph of those 15 trials and write your story as a goblin miner.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >3 explorable levels</h2><br>Explore 3 mines packed with traps and riches.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125920/extras/6d6adb69999c0f88b16c18eb2f9004b6.poster.avif?t=1663345602\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125920/extras/6d6adb69999c0f88b16c18eb2f9004b6.webm?t=1663345602\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125920/extras/6d6adb69999c0f88b16c18eb2f9004b6.mp4?t=1663345602\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A dynamic platformer</h2><br>Optimize the use of your grappling gun and rocket boots to be as quick as a true goblin.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125920/extras/3a2c9a145f853435b68d9cb7867ba82d.poster.avif?t=1663345602\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125920/extras/3a2c9a145f853435b68d9cb7867ba82d.webm?t=1663345602\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125920/extras/3a2c9a145f853435b68d9cb7867ba82d.mp4?t=1663345602\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Become a master miner</h2><br>Complete challenges to unlock the gear of the miner masters.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125920/extras/2b7b539f324d205fb358830e8cb81efa.poster.avif?t=1663345602\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125920/extras/2b7b539f324d205fb358830e8cb81efa.webm?t=1663345602\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125920/extras/2b7b539f324d205fb358830e8cb81efa.mp4?t=1663345602\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Mining Odyssey is a dynamic platformer game in first person view.<br><br>Take your pickaxe and grappling gun and challenge 15 successive timed trials, in which you will have to gather a set list of ores in a hostile environment.<br><br>Explore, discover, memorize, die and retry. With each try, get closer to your goal and dive deeper in harder trials.<br><br>Triumph of those 15 trials and write your story as a goblin miner.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >3 explorable levels</h2><br>Explore 3 mines packed with traps and riches.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125920/extras/6d6adb69999c0f88b16c18eb2f9004b6.poster.avif?t=1663345602\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125920/extras/6d6adb69999c0f88b16c18eb2f9004b6.webm?t=1663345602\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125920/extras/6d6adb69999c0f88b16c18eb2f9004b6.mp4?t=1663345602\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A dynamic platformer</h2><br>Optimize the use of your grappling gun and rocket boots to be as quick as a true goblin.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125920/extras/3a2c9a145f853435b68d9cb7867ba82d.poster.avif?t=1663345602\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125920/extras/3a2c9a145f853435b68d9cb7867ba82d.webm?t=1663345602\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125920/extras/3a2c9a145f853435b68d9cb7867ba82d.mp4?t=1663345602\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Become a master miner</h2><br>Complete challenges to unlock the gear of the miner masters.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125920/extras/2b7b539f324d205fb358830e8cb81efa.poster.avif?t=1663345602\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125920/extras/2b7b539f324d205fb358830e8cb81efa.webm?t=1663345602\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125920/extras/2b7b539f324d205fb358830e8cb81efa.mp4?t=1663345602\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
